{{!-- Sitewide "Support the work" CTA rendered under posts, the about
     page, and anywhere else the partial is invoked. Hidden for
     paid/comped members and the staff preview email — they've
     already subscribed. Always shown for free Subscribers AND
     anonymous visitors (both should be converted).

     The {{#match @member.email @custom.dashboard_preview_email}}
     check used to live at the outer level, which was a bug:
     when both sides were empty (anonymous visitor + unset preview
     email setting), the match returned true and the CTA was
     hidden from anonymous visitors entirely. Now gated behind
     {{#if @member}} so the email match only runs when there's an
     actual signed-in member to compare against. --}}
{{#match @member.status "paid"}}{{else}}
{{#match @member.status "comped"}}{{else}}
{{#if @member}}{{#match @member.email @custom.dashboard_preview_email}}{{else}}
{{> "membership-cta-body"}}
{{/match}}{{else}}
{{> "membership-cta-body"}}
{{/if}}
{{/match}}
{{/match}}
